Olayinka Sanni (ka amụrụ n'ọnwa Ọgọstụ 21, n'afọ 1986) bụ onye egwuregwu bọọlụ bọọlụ Naịjirịa na Amerịka. A mụrụ ya na Chicago Heights, Illinois, n'oge na-adịbeghị anya, ọ gbara ọkwa etiti / ike n'ihu maka Phoenix Mercury na WNBA nakwa maka Charleville-Méz na France - LFB
N'afọ ya nke okenye na West Virginia, Sanni nwetara akara dị elu na akara kwa egwuregwu (16.2) na rebound kwa egwuregwu (7.1).
A họpụtara Sanni na 18th n'ozuzu ya na 2008 WNBA Draft site na Detroit Shock
N'ime egwuregwu iri atọ na otu ọ gbara n'oge bọọlụ ya, ọ malitere egwuregwu itoolu
Ọ gbara kpọmkwem 50% site n'ala (41-82) mgbe ọ na-eme nkezi obere ihe karịrị nkeji iri kwa egwuregwu.
Ọ na-agbara Calais na France bọọlụ n'oge 2008–09 WNBA off-season.
Ọ na-egwuri egwu ugbu a maka ESB Villeneuve-d'Ascq na France n'oge 2009–10 WNBA off-season.
Olayinka Sanni na-elekọta Olayinka Sanni Foundation, nke na-abụghị maka uru nke na-elekọta mmepe nke ụmụ nwoke na ụmụ nwanyị site na ndu na ogige basketball
N'afọ 2017, ọ kwadoro ogige basketball maka ụmụ nwoke na ụmụ nwanyị nọ n'afọ iri na ụma na Lagos, Nigeria.
